How does your body manage blood pressure?

2
00:00:02,800 --> 00:00:05,200
It’s more complex than you think.

3
00:00:05,200 --> 00:00:10,000
Blood pressure regulation involves your heart, blood vessels, and kidneys working together.

4
00:00:10,000 --> 00:00:14,000
But what happens when this system is thrown off balance?

5
00:00:14,000 --> 00:00:17,200
Factors like stress and diet play a role.

6
00:00:17,200 --> 00:00:21,600
Studies show high blood pressure can lead to serious health issues.

7
00:00:21,600 --> 00:00:23,200
Yet many remain unaware.

8
00:00:23,200 --> 00:00:27,600
Understanding this regulation can empower you to make better health choices.

